				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\delta$$\end{document}]. I is the stack current, F is Faradayâs constant, N is the number of cells, x7,O2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
